Package: IBMR
Title: Instrument Borrowing for Mendelian Randomization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Anagh", "Chattopadhyay", 
           email = "achatto4@jh.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for borrowing genetic instruments across datasets in 
    Mendelian randomization analyses. Includes methods for assessing 
    coheterogeneity, multidimensional mode-based estimation, and 
    MR-PRESSO with instrument borrowing.
